Here's your **Gold Fundamentals XAU/USD Scalping Terminal** — fully built and ready for a developer to wire up.

**What's inside:**

**Live Chart** — Dynamic candlestick chart with real-time price ticks, OHLC overlay, M1/M5/M15/H1 timeframe switching, and current price line.

**Deposit System** — Full form collecting name, bank (all SA banks listed), account number, and ZAR amount. On first deposit, the account is **locked as the linked account** — all future withdrawals go only to that same account.

**Withdrawal System** — Automatically shows the linked bank details (masked account number). Blocks withdrawals if no deposit has been made. Validates against available balance.

**Trading** — BUY/SELL with configurable lot size, stop loss, and take profit. Auto-closes on TP/SL hit with P&L calculated in ZAR. Full trade history table with win rate.

**Order Book** — Live simulated ask/bid depth with spread display.

